[fire crackles,
indistinct chatter]

13:10.357 --> 13:12.257
- [pensive sigh]

13:13.426 --> 13:15.093
- [laughs]

13:17.464 --> 13:19.163
- [sighs]

13:19.166 --> 13:21.499
[indistinct chatter]

13:25.305 --> 13:26.904
- What are ye two on a date,
are ye?

